snippet.title: The King of Fighters XIV - Blue Mary Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
The King of Fighters XIV tournament continues with new DLC characters! With one of the biggest rosters ever, create the perfect team in the classic 3-on-3 battle system. Burn to Fight!
